seven and a half hours

00:01:02.168 --> 00:01:03.544
of every day.

00:01:03.544 --> 00:01:05.552
Also, there will be re-performance

00:01:05.552 --> 00:01:09.030
of five of my performances,
some of which I made

00:01:09.030 --> 00:01:11.833
in seventies and eighties,
and they're going

00:01:11.833 --> 00:01:15.717
to re-perform the same amount
of time, like three months.

00:01:15.717 --> 00:01:18.200
So this kind of thing's
never been done til now,

00:01:18.200 --> 00:01:20.530
so it's a really big experiment.

00:01:20.530 --> 00:01:24.016
