something's terribly wrong,

00:01:30.896 --> 00:01:33.812
because it means that my work
doesn't communicate anywhere,

00:01:33.812 --> 00:01:35.513
that means it's dead.

00:01:35.513 --> 00:01:38.678
There was a very funny
interview of Leonard Cohen,

00:01:38.678 --> 00:01:41.517
and he say, "I am now in a third act,"

00:01:41.517 --> 00:01:44.179
and in third act,
everything start very well,

00:01:44.179 --> 00:01:46.382
but in the end, the main actor die.

00:01:46.382 --> 00:01:49.683
I also feel that I'm in a
kind of third act right now,

00:01:49.683 --> 00:01:53.315
you know, (mumbing) MoMA,
it's finishing a huge amount

00:01:53.315 --> 00:01:57.147
of work, which is very
interesting about legacy,

00:01:57.147 --> 00:02:00.216
what you going to leave after you die.

00:02:00.216 --> 00:02:03.161
But one thing you can leave
always is a good idea,

00:02:03.161 --> 00:02:07.724
and I really wanted to have
this good idea to live after me.

